msgctxt "54346b5e3b4d4cb885104c5730f15afd"
msgid "The Threefold Ritual"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "faaa2cecfce440859f40f055c63cb39f"
msgid ""
"Brahmā, great king Śakra, gods and nāgas, Yakṣas, gandharvas, uragas, "
"asuras, Garuḍas, kumbhāṇḍas, kinnaras, All beings who are sons of the "
"Sugata, Accept these seven wonderful and resplendent jewels and listen to "
"me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "983cc021a9de4d80926f363cdae1c3d1"
msgid "The qualities of the blessed Buddha are inconceivable."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9fa12f8757ab4b9c8226afdcee018108"
msgid "The qualities of the holy Dharma are inconceivable."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88f2cc13939d42eb9c404c42f7a971e1"
msgid "The qualities of the noble Saṅgha are inconceivable."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "03c4c037bc1f4c86bec2d80d00b019a7"
msgid ""
"The unsurpassed fruition of true faith In the inconceivable Three Jewels is "
"inconceivable."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "b68f1520e51c48f2a18325f85e553a8f"
msgid ""
"It is rare to hear so much as the names of the Three Jewels, Even over the "
"course of millions of eons."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8a641f20f2a442a080bc783bf5037cc5"
msgid ""
"Now that you have taken such a rare embodiment endowed with the freedoms, "
"Use the energy of your magical abilities and faith to approach, And listen "
"to the profound teaching of the Victor In this sanctuary bedecked with the "
"jewels of liberation."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "acc0d35a0efd421ab4cb8d4a79c5996a"
msgid ""
"May those who gather here intent upon the holy Dharma, Such as powerful "
"gods, nāgas, yakṣas, and the like, Accept this share of Dharma merit:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2881660451f64d50b49a033e0ce03f75"
msgid ""
"we dedicate it So that you may increase in splendor and retinue and "
"accomplish what you desire."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4786584e3b684de1b95637d3495694ee"
msgid ""
"May you obtain the nectar of the teachings, Bring prosperity to each and "
"every class of beings wherever they are, And protect the teachings of the "
"tathāgatas."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "041e69d0a6b64bf68c624c7e73363c40"
msgid "This concludes “The Threefold Ritual.”"
msgstr ""
